\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {1}{\ignorespaces Overview of LLM-Flax\xspace  . Given only a PDDL domain file, Stage~1 automatically generates relaxation and complementary rules; Stage~2 provides budget-aware LLM failure recovery; and Stage~3 replaces the domain-trained GNN with zero-shot LLM object scoring. Together, the full Full LLM-Flax\xspace  system deploys on a new domain with no manual engineering.}}{2}{figure.caption.1}\protected@file@percent }
